		<h1 class="entry-title">Short Film: Singularity</h1>
		<p class="meta post-meta">Posted on <span class="updated">September 21, 2014</span>  by <span class="vcard author"><a class="fn" href="http://www.sfsignal.com/archives/author/john/">John DeNardo</a></span>  in <a href="http://www.sfsignal.com/archives/category/movies/" rel="category tag">Movies</a> // 0 Comments</p>
	</header>
		<div class="entry clearfix">
				<div align="center"><img border="0" src="//i2.wp.com/www.sfsignal.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/singularity-short-film.jpg?w=620" class="justBorder" data-recalc-dims="1"/></div>
<p>&#8220;An architect with OCD must fight to keep control of his mind after he is implanted with an overprotective AI&#8230;&#8221;</p>
<p><span id="more-100146"></span></p>
<div class="clearer"></div>
